C4Component
    title Component Diagram - API & Application Layer (Inside Settlement Core API)

    Container_Boundary(api_boundary, "API Container (ASP.NET Core 10.0)") {
        Component(rate_limit, "Rate Limiting Middleware", "System.Threading.RateLimiting", "Protects against API abuse (Token Bucket).")
        Component(cmd_handlers, "Command Handlers", "MediatR", "Orchestrates command execution flow.")
        Component(aggregates, "Aggregates", "Domain Model", "Enforces business rules and emits events.")
        Component(marten_store, "Event Store Client", "Marten / Npgsql", "Handles atomic event persistence (Optimistic Concurrency).")
        Component(resilience, "Resilience Policies", "Polly / Infrastructure", "Circuit breakers, Retries with Jitter, Timeouts.")
        Component(outbox_dispatch, "Outbox Dispatcher", "MediatR / Background", "Ensures eventual consistency for external integrations.")
    }

    Rel(rate_limit, cmd_handlers, "Passes Request", "MediatR")
    Rel(cmd_handlers, resilience, "Wraps Logic", "Polly Policies")
    Rel(resilience, aggregates, "Applies State Changes", "C# Methods")
    Rel(aggregates, marten_store, "Appends Events", "Marten DSL")
    Rel(cmd_handlers, outbox_dispatch, "Records Outbox Message", "Shared Transaction")

    Note right of marten_store: Version-based Optimistic Concurrency Control.
    Note left of resilience: Circuit Breaker trips after 5 consecutive failures.
    Note bottom of cmd_handlers: Each handler is scoped to a single request/transaction.
